          "reviewBody": "I am extremely disappointed with the lack of professionalism and transparency at Indraprastha Global School.\nDespite multiple follow-ups, I have not received my security deposit refund. The school has stopped responding to my calls, and I feel duped as a parent. I urge the management to address this issue immediately and show accountability towards their commitments. It’s frustrating when schools fail to maintain basic ethical standards. I hope this review serves as a caution to other parents considering this institution.",
