          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "This school's commitment to excellence is truly commendable. They have a progressive approach to education, embracing the latest technology to enhance learning. The opportunities provided to students are unparalleled, ensuring a well-rounded education. The individual attention given by the dedicated teachers fosters a supportive learning environment. The exposure to new, advanced technology and state-of-the-art facilities keeps students at the forefront of education. The educators here are not just teachers; they are mentors who are passionate, motivated, and truly care about each student's success. The emphasis on teaching ethics and morals adds a valuable dimension to the education they offer. This school truly stands out as a place of excellence in education.I wholeheartedly recommend this exceptional school to anyone seeking a top-notch educational experience.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Indraprastha GLOBAL School - Sector 93B"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "PUSHPA YADAV"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-10-29",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Indraprastha Global School, Noida  is an institution that truly prioritizes the growth and well-being of both students and educators. The collaborative spirit among faculty members is palpable, fostering an environment of continuous learning and innovation. The school's commitment to academic excellence is evident in its robust curriculum. It not only provides a solid foundation in core subjects but also encourages critical thinking and creativity. This balanced approach empowers students to excel academically while nurturing their individual strengths and interests. Furthermore, the emphasis on extracurricular activities is commendable. Students are encouraged to explore their passions beyond the classroom, whether it be in sports, arts, or various clubs. This not only enriches their overall educational experience but also helps foster a sense of belonging.\nThe administration's open-door policy and receptiveness to feedback create a culture of mutual respect and collaboration. This transparency not only benefits the teachers but ultimately contributes to a positive learning environment for the students.\nTo summarise it all, Indraprastha Global School, Noida is a place where passion for teaching is met with equal enthusiasm for learning.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
